{
  "info": {
    "name": "Challenge Tech - Dimensa",
    "description": "API de web crawler de frases — quotes.toscrape.com",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sign Up",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"usuario@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/sign_up",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "sign_up"]
            },
            "description": "Cria um novo usuário e retorna o token de acesso.\n\nResposta esperada (201):\n{\n  \"token\": \"abc123...\"\n}"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token salvo:', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign In",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"usuario@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/sign_in",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "sign_in"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica o usuário e retorna um novo token de acesso.\n\nResposta esperada (200):\n{\n  \"token\": \"abc123...\"\n}\n\nErro (401):\n{\n  \"error\": \"Invalid email or password\"\n}"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token salvo:', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Quotes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Buscar quotes por tag",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/quotes/love",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "quotes", "love"]
            },
            "description": "Busca frases pela tag informada na URL.\n\n- 1ª requisição: crawla o site e salva no MongoDB\n- Requisições seguintes: retorna do cache (MongoDB)\n- Tag sem resultados: tenta crawlar novamente\n\nResposta esperada (200):\n{\n  \"quotes\": [\n    {\n      \"quote\": \"texto da frase\",\n      \"author\": \"nome do autor\",\n      \"author_about\": \"http://quotes.toscrape.com/author/...\",\n      \"tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\"]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nSem token (401):\n{\n  \"error\": \"Unauthorized\"\n}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Buscar quotes por tag (sem token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/quotes/love",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "quotes", "love"]
            },
            "description": "Demonstra que o endpoint é protegido. Deve retornar 401."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
  ]
}
